  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nWhen pasting in a serialised raw transaction in the `Broadcast Transaction` tab, the chainId parameter isn't validated against the current network when it should be.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Get a  serialised raw transaction \r\n2. Paste it in the `Broadcast Transaction` component on a different network than the tx was signed on\r\n3. Box does not turn invalid when it should\r\n4. No error message displayed either\r\n\r\n",
